parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electronic brake system can cause the brakes to malfunction, leading to a loss of stopping power, which can result in accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: The brake pedal travels to the floor
the brakes do not respond as normal
the vehicle is difficult to stop
the brakes make a grinding noise
the brake warning light illuminates on the dashboard.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The excessive brightness of the low beam headlights can cause glare to oncoming traffic, leading to potentially hazardous driving conditions, including accidents and near-misses.
symptoms: The low beam headlights are too bright
causing glare to oncoming traffic
constant flashing from other drivers
and temporary blindness from oncoming vehicles.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the camshaft lifters can cause a rough engine idle, ticking sounds, and potentially lead to catalytic converter failure, which can result in hazardous emissions and further damage to the vehicle if not addressed promptly.
symptoms: Rough engine idle
ticking sounds from the engine
potential catalytic converter failure.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The obstruction of the moon roof drain line can cause water to leak into the vehicle, potentially damaging electrical components and leading to malfunctions, which can pose a hazard in emergency situations.
symptoms: Water dripping from the moon roof
water leaking onto the electronics package under the driver's side dash
malfunctioning electronic components
driver becoming locked in the vehicle due to wet electronics.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Improper Service Repair of Moon Roof Drain Line
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Improper service repair of the moon roof drain line can cause further damage to the vehicle, leading to electrical malfunctions and potential hazards.
symptoms: Bursting of the drain line
water leaking onto electrical components
malfunctioning electronic components
driver becoming locked in the vehicle due to wet electronics.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Sudden and unexplained windshield cracking can impair the driver's visibility, leading to accidents, and may also compromise the structural integrity of the vehicle.
symptoms: Cracks or shattering of the windshield without any apparent external damage or impact
cracks may appear suddenly and without warning
cracks may be located in the middle or bottom of the windshield.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Defects in the windshield manufacturing process can lead to spontaneous cracking or shattering, impairing the driver's visibility and potentially causing accidents.
symptoms: Cracks or shattering of the windshield without any apparent external damage or impact
cracks may appear suddenly and without warning
cracks may be located in the middle or bottom of the windshield.
